StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [GetActyResultComments]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
@RecruiterID uniqueidentifier, @StartDate date.me, @EndDate date.me
AS BEGIN
SET TRANSACTION ISOLATION LEVEL READ UNCOMMITTED
SELECT ID, RecruiterId, StartDate, EndDate, RecruiterComments, SncoicComments, RecruiterCommentsSigned, SncoicCommentsSigned FROM RSSOSS.USMC.RecruiterAc.vityAndResult WHERE RecruiterID=@RecruiterID AND StartDate = @StartDate AND EndDate = @EndDate END
